headline: Lam Research Targets AI Growth With CEA Leti Deal And Leadership Shift
summary: Lam Research (NasdaqGS:LRCX) has entered a new multi year collaboration with CEA Leti to work on advanced specialty technology devices for AI and high performance computing. The partnership focuses on MEMS, 3D imaging, RF solutions, photonics, and quantum optics, aiming to speed up materials and device development.
